                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                        </head>
                        <p>The agreement on aid to Turkey was signed at Ankara by Ambassador Wilson
                            and Turkish Prime Minister Saka on July 12, 1947; for text, see
                            Department of State Treaties and Other International Acts Series No.
                            1629, or 61 Stat. (pt. 3) 2953.</p>
